  Source:
    Title: Young India
    Editor: M. K. Gandhi
    Locus:
      Date: 23 January 1930
---
I am giving you a bit of my experience and that of my companions when I
say that he who has experienced the magic of prayer may do without food
for days together but not a single moment without prayer. For without
prayer there is no inward peace.
